      "about": "Mesus Ravenwell is a skilled flakanner warrior and war veteran from House Ravenwell. Born to Maier and Airola Ravenwell, his distant connection to the noble line led him to train among merchant children. At age seven, he was kidnapped by Rouvyr Tribals but escaped after three days of survival in the mountains. After a decade in Ivéria serving as a man-at-arms for Corina Mankett and a brief stint as a sharpshooter in the war against Ymaras, the twenty-year-old Mesus has arrived in Elirium seeking glory and a place in the Adventurer's Guild.",
